Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: San Francisco transport strike
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z99ks
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 18 Apr 1976
San Francisco transport workers' pay demands redefine accepted pay differentials. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.